> My old 65 double door had mixed bumpers, pointed rear
> and slash front. They were the original bumpers on the
> bus. It only had 2 owners so i was able to ask the
> question. It was originally owned by Pete Lovely, a
> local VW dealer. He said that VW switched bumpers in
> 65 but had more front slash than rear slash due to
> having to replace more rears than frontsfrom
> accidents, so a few vehicles came with a mix of both
> bumpers until they got the numbers down on front
> slash.


